Information[edit]

Format[edit]

  • Hero Bans
    • Each team bans 1 hero per map, with the ban impacting both teams.
    • Each ban must be from a different role than the other team's ban.
    • Teams can only ban a hero once per series, but may repeat a ban from the opposing team.
  • Group Stage: December 11th - 16th
    • Round robin with 2 groups
    • All matches are Ft3
    • Top 2 teams from each group advance to Playoffs
  • Playoffs: December 19th - 22nd
    • Double elimination bracket
    • Upper Bracket Quarterfinals and Semifinals are Ft3
    • Entire Lower Bracket, Upper Bracket Final, and Grand Finals are Ft4
    • Team Falcons and Crazy Raccoon start in Upper Bracket Semifinals

properties.*: Soop Overwatch Cup Season 2 - Korea is an offline Korean OW2 tournament organized by WDG and SOOP. This A-Tier tournament took place from Dec 11 to 22 2024 featuring 10 teams competing over a total prize pool of ₩30,000,000 KRW.
